<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>密码错误 - GUCCANG</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #f8f0e3;
            --secondary-color: #eadbc8;
            --accent-color: #e76f51;
            --accent-hover: #f4a261;
            --text-color: #433520;
            --bg-color: #faf6f0;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --border-color: #ddd0c0;
            --shadow-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            --error-color: #e63946;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .error-container {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px var(--shadow-color);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--error-color);
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--error-color);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-color);
            opacity: 0.7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .blog-name {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-message {
            background: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            color: #721c24;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .retry-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            background: var(--accent-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .retry-btn:hover {
            background: var(--accent-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--shadow-color);
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            color: var(--accent-hover);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .tips {
            background: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            color: #0c5460;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .tips ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .tips li {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .error-container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
                margin: 20px;
            }
            
            .title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .subtitle {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="icon">❌</div>
        <h1 class="title">密码错误</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">访问密码不正确，请重新输入</p>
        
        <div class="blog-name">{{.BLOGNAME}}</div>
        
        <div class="error-message">
            <strong>错误：</strong> 您输入的密码不正确，无法访问此日记。
        </div>

        <div class="tips">
            <strong>提示：</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>请确认密码输入正确</li>
                <li>密码区分大小写</li>
                <li>如果忘记密码，请联系管理员</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <a href="/get?blogname={{.BLOGNAME}}" class="retry-btn">
            🔄 重新输入密码
        </a>
        
        <a href="/link" class="back-link">← 返回主页</a>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 3秒后自动跳转到重试页面
        setTimeout(function() {
            const retryBtn = document.querySelector('.retry-btn');
            if (retryBtn) {
                retryBtn.style.background = 'var(--accent-hover)';
                retryBtn.innerHTML = '🔄 正在跳转...';
                setTimeout(function() {
                    window.location.href = retryBtn.href;
                }, 1000);
            }
        }, 3000);
    </script>
</body>
</html> 